GET     /driver/me                          [DONE]
        -> View Logged-in Driver Profile

PATCH   /driver/me                          [DONE]
        -> Update Driver Profile (phoneNumber, vehicleNumber)

GET     /driver/rides/pending               [DONE]
        -> View All PENDING Ride Requests from Students
        -> Driver picks one to accept

PATCH   /driver/ride/{rideId}/accept        [DONE]
        -> Accept a Pending Ride
        -> Sets driver = current driver
        -> Sets status = ACCEPTED
        -> Throws if ride is not PENDING
        -> Throws if ride already has a driver

GET     /driver/ride/{rideId}                [DONE]
        -> View ride with {rideId} which driver accepted earlier
        -> Includes student details

GET     /driver/ride/history                [DONE]
        -> View All Rides by this Driver
